label.value: sacrum length

value.value: The length on the ventral side of a fused sacrum along the proximal-distal axis.
This is measured from the cranial borders of the wings to the centroventral border of the body of the last vertebra.

label.value: sacrum physiological length

value.value: The length of the body of a fused sacrum on the ventral side along the proximal-distal axis.
This is measured between the centers of the bodies of the most cranial and most caudal vertebrae.

label.value: sacrum breadth

value.value: The width of a fused sacrum along the medial-lateral axis.

label.value: sacrum cranial articular surface breadth

value.value: The width of the cranial articular surface of a fused sacrum along the medial-lateral axis.

label.value: sacrum cranial articular surface height

value.value: The height of the cranial articular surface of a fused sacrum along the ventral-dorsal axis.

label.value: thoracic vertebra physiological length

value.value: The length of the body of a thoracic vertebra along the superior-inferior axis.
This is measured between the centers of the facies terminalis cranialis and the facies terminalis caudalis.

label.value: thoracic vertebra transverse process breadth

value.value: The width between a left and right transverse process along the medial-lateral axis.

label.value: thoracic vertebra cranial articular surface breadth

value.value: The width of the cranial articular surface of a thoracic vertebra along the medial-lateral axis.

label.value: thoracic vertebra caudal articular surface breadth

value.value: The width of the caudal articular surface of a thoracic vertebra along the medial-lateral axis.
